<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 donation-header">
    <%= link_to root_url do %>
      <%= image_tag('noisebridge_logo.jpg', class: 'center noisebridge_logo') %>
    <% end %>
    <h3>Noisebridge: a hackerspace needs your help!</h3>
    <p>Our 2169 Mission Street lease is up in August and we're in a crunch to find a new space and increase the amount of money we have to be able to afford the new space. We need # million dollars to buy or # thousand dollars to lease a new space. Please make a donation now, and setup a recurring monthly donation, to support non-profit donation based open to the public Hacking in San Francisco.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2 donation-form">
      <%= render "donation_form" %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4 clo-md-offset-2 summary">
      <div class="table-container">
        <%= render "recent_donations" %>
      </div>

      <div class="table-container">
        <%= render "current_projects" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
